</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="F0F26FBA3ECB0623E033E7943330F827" pageId="96" pageNumber="96" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="3BF29CCDE4EED6C4105CCF18F8E5FDDF" pageId="96" pageNumber="96">Specimens of this species have the golden pubescence usually more or less obliterated.</paragraph>
